00:04:13.419 --> 00:04:15.296
He was framed and owed a lot of money.

00:04:15.296 --> 00:04:16.881
I wanted to help him.

00:04:18.883 --> 00:04:22.095
Actually, I also thought
the baby was his at first.

00:04:22.095 --> 00:04:23.971
But I didn't expect...

00:04:29.852 --> 00:04:31.645
Surprised?

00:04:33.398 --> 00:04:35.065
Very.

00:04:36.276 --> 00:04:39.112
I'm surprised you're so honest with me.

00:04:39.112 --> 00:04:41.280
Actually, lying is very lonely.

00:04:42.448 --> 00:04:44.909
I also want to be understood.

00:04:46.995 --> 00:04:49.371
I might not be able to understand you,

00:04:51.666 --> 00:04:54.043
but I will always support you.

00:05:01.301 --> 00:05:03.928
I don't want Gu Hou Ze to know the truth.

00:05:04.762 --> 00:05:06.848
I also don't want to give up
the management rights.

00:05:06.848 --> 00:05:09.684
So, even if Chairman Wu doesn't support us,

00:05:09.684 --> 00:05:10.685
it doesn't matter.

00:05:10.685 --> 00:05:14.439
We still have Qian Xiao An's
kickback case to investigate.

00:05:14.439 --> 00:05:17.276
And Chaomai's public takeover, too.

00:05:17.276 --> 00:05:19.485
