00:05:19.485 --> 00:05:21.028
We have to persevere.

00:05:26.075 --> 00:05:27.869
What about you?

00:05:27.869 --> 00:05:29.870
How's Xin Yi Fu doing?

00:05:35.460 --> 00:05:37.419
We had a big fight.

00:05:42.008 --> 00:05:44.844
Is what he said about Lin Feng Hua true?

00:05:45.511 --> 00:05:48.139
He said they're just working partners.

00:05:48.139 --> 00:05:49.557
Do you believe him?

00:05:53.019 --> 00:05:54.478
To be honest...

00:05:55.980 --> 00:05:58.649
It's hard for me to believe him.

00:05:59.734 --> 00:06:01.485
But if I don't believe him...

00:06:02.945 --> 00:06:04.613
I can't do it either.

00:06:06.995 --> 00:06:10.164
I've been thinking about it
since the article came out.

00:06:10.164 --> 00:06:13.375
Maybe the problem is between us.

00:06:14.877 --> 00:06:18.256
I've been thinking about it every day.

00:06:18.256 --> 00:06:20.842
Is he happy with me?

00:06:20.842 --> 00:06:23.385
Am I restricting him?

00:06:27.098 --> 00:06:30.017
If you can't let go, don't force yourself to.

00:06:30.893 --> 00:06:32.394
It's okay.

00:06:33.896 --> 00:06:37.025
If you want to be with him,

00:06:37.025 --> 00:06:39.276
then trust him completely.

00:06:44.949 --> 00:06:46.576
Dr. Gu, can you please get out of the car?

00:06:46.576 --> 00:06:48.202
Dr. Gu, do you have anything to say today?

00:06:48.202 --> 00:06:51.080
Dr. Gu, can you comment on the news report?

00:06:51.080 --> 00:06:52.540
Dr. Gu, before Ms. Zhou married Mr. Zhan,

00:06:52.540 --> 00:06:54.292
you knew she was pregnant, right?

00:06:54.292 --> 00:06:57.128
Did she tell you she was pregnant
before marriage, or did you support her?

00:06:57.128 --> 00:06:59.001
How could you let Ms. Zhou marry Mr. Zhan?

00:06:59.001 --> 00:07:00.670
Do you only target rich women?

00:07:00.670 --> 00:07:03.423
Do you always mess with your patients?

00:07:03.423 --> 00:07:05.550
Why did you snatch the microphone?
Are you feeling guilty?

00:07:05.550 --> 00:07:06.717
Do you have anything to say?

00:07:06.717 --> 00:07:08.511
How could you lose your temper as a doctor?

00:07:08.511 --> 00:07:09.720
Are you angry out of embarrassment?

00:07:09.720 --> 00:07:11.514
Dr. Gu, please comment.

00:07:11.514 --> 00:07:13.464
Don't you have any morals?

00:07:14.684 --> 00:07:16.310
It's in the news.

00:07:16.310 --> 00:07:18.604
How long do you want to keep her here?

00:07:18.604 --> 00:07:19.647
Mr. Wei.

00:07:19.647 --> 00:07:22.316
I know you want Ms. Fan to be discharged.

00:07:22.316 --> 00:07:26.195
But there are professional procedures
for patients to be admitted or discharged.

00:07:26.195 --> 00:07:29.699
We can't simply judge
based on the magazine's report.

00:07:29.699 --> 00:07:33.619
But you can't say she's delusional
and keep her here.

00:07:33.619 --> 00:07:35.288
Please give me some time.

00:07:35.288 --> 00:07:38.040
I'll get some experts to evaluate this with me.

00:07:38.040 --> 00:07:40.647
I'll give you an explanation then.

00:07:42.462 --> 00:07:44.630
Can I go see Yue Jiao now?

00:07:45.882 --> 00:07:48.384
Ever since this news came out,

00:07:48.384 --> 00:07:51.470
Ms. Fan has been getting
more and more out of control.

00:07:52.346 --> 00:07:56.142
She even had to be sedated
by a nurse last night.

00:07:56.142 --> 00:07:59.437
I'm afraid if you visit her now
and bring this up,

00:07:59.437 --> 00:08:01.639
things will only get worse.

00:08:04.233 --> 00:08:06.944
Then can I ask you to
handle this as soon as possible?

00:08:06.944 --> 00:08:09.071
Of course, I will.

00:08:20.583 --> 00:08:23.211
Hello, Grandma.

00:08:23.211 --> 00:08:25.072
Did you have your follow-up appointment today?

00:08:25.072 --> 00:08:26.881
What did the doctor say?

00:08:26.881 --> 00:08:29.050
That's what the doctor said.

00:08:29.050 --> 00:08:31.677
He told me to relax.

00:08:31.677 --> 00:08:34.889
I just need to go back for regular checkups.

00:08:34.889 --> 00:08:37.391
I'm fine. Don't worry.

00:08:37.391 --> 00:08:40.853
You have to eat three meals a day in Taipei.

00:08:40.853 --> 00:08:43.189
I saw the photo you sent me.

00:08:43.189 --> 00:08:44.857
You look thinner.

00:08:44.857 --> 00:08:47.735
Yes, I'm eating.

00:08:47.735 --> 00:08:50.530
You have to keep the money from me safe.

00:08:50.530 --> 00:08:52.073
I know.

00:08:52.073 --> 00:08:53.991
How's your life in Taipei?

00:08:53.991 --> 00:08:55.826
Is your boss good to you?

00:08:55.826 --> 00:08:59.789
He's very good to me. Don't worry.

00:08:59.789 --> 00:09:03.251
He's the one who rented my place for me.

00:09:03.251 --> 00:09:06.837
He even sent me on a business trip
to Singapore recently.

00:09:06.837 --> 00:09:08.673
I can go abroad for fun.

00:09:08.673 --> 00:09:10.675
Isn't that great?

00:09:10.675 --> 00:09:12.593
That's great.

00:09:12.593 --> 00:09:15.555
Then go and have fun.

00:09:15.555 --> 00:09:16.597
All right.

00:09:16.597 --> 00:09:19.976
Stop chatting while you're working.

00:09:19.976 --> 00:09:21.602
All right, that's all.

00:09:21.602 --> 00:09:24.021
Okay, bye.

00:09:24.021 --> 00:09:25.773
Bye, Grandma.

00:09:25.773 --> 00:09:27.274
Bye.

00:09:30.945 --> 00:09:36.814
