00:10:54.779 --> 00:10:55.946
Thank you.

00:10:57.573 --> 00:11:01.160
Excuse me, is this Xiao Ting Yun's old home?

00:11:01.160 --> 00:11:02.620
What's the matter?

00:11:02.620 --> 00:11:05.998
I'm Ting Yun's colleague.
I was wondering if she's back.

00:11:05.998 --> 00:11:06.999
No, it's nothing.

00:11:06.999 --> 00:11:08.876
I just talked to
her on the phone.

00:11:08.876 --> 00:11:10.919
She's working in Taipei.

00:11:11.921 --> 00:11:14.840
Did something happen to her?

00:11:14.840 --> 00:11:16.967
No, it's nothing.

00:11:16.967 --> 00:11:19.220
I just happened to be nearby,
so I thought I'd drop by.

00:11:19.220 --> 00:11:21.389
- I see.
- Yes.

00:11:21.389 --> 00:11:22.848
Thank you for your help.

00:11:22.848 --> 00:11:24.517
It's lunchtime now.

00:11:24.517 --> 00:11:25.805
I have some dishes in the kitchen.

00:11:25.805 --> 00:11:27.103
Let's eat together.

00:11:27.103 --> 00:11:28.270
No, it's okay.

00:11:28.270 --> 00:11:29.939
- I don't want to trouble you.
- It's okay.

00:11:29.939 --> 00:11:32.441
I'm the only old person here.

00:11:32.441 --> 00:11:33.484
I'm lonely.

00:11:33.484 --> 00:11:35.403
Just eat with me.

00:11:35.403 --> 00:11:37.113
Come on, don't be shy.

00:11:37.113 --> 00:11:38.489
Let's go. My hands are dirty.

00:11:38.489 --> 00:11:39.490
- It's okay.
- Let's go together.

00:11:39.490 --> 00:11:40.783
Okay, thank you.

00:11:40.783 --> 00:11:42.201
Come on, let's go in.

00:11:42.201 --> 00:11:44.978
Grandma, you're too friendly.

00:11:53.796 --> 00:11:55.339
Dr. Gu.

00:12:01.595 --> 00:12:02.888
What is it?

00:12:03.597 --> 00:12:06.433
I want to quit.

00:12:15.025 --> 00:12:16.519
Why?

00:12:18.696 --> 00:12:23.033
After the news broke,
all the patients canceled.

00:12:23.033 --> 00:12:27.527
I guess the clinic doesn't need me anymore.

00:12:31.041 --> 00:12:32.334
Okay.

00:12:56.734 --> 00:12:58.026
Hello.

00:12:59.028 --> 00:13:00.445
Is everything okay?

00:13:01.781 --> 00:13:04.408
I'm fine. How about you?

00:13:05.493 --> 00:13:08.746
I ran into reporters at the clinic again today.

00:13:08.746 --> 00:13:11.057
I think I'll stay at a hotel for a few days.

00:13:11.957 --> 00:13:13.250
Okay.

00:13:14.210 --> 00:13:15.502
You've been through a lot.

00:13:16.712 --> 00:13:18.213
I've been thinking...

00:13:19.173 --> 00:13:21.133
How about this?

00:13:21.133 --> 00:13:23.385
You resign as chairperson.

00:13:23.385 --> 00:13:25.846
We'll move somewhere no one knows us.

00:13:26.472 --> 00:13:28.182
We'll register our marriage.

00:13:28.182 --> 00:13:30.267
And have the baby.

00:13:31.644 --> 00:13:34.094
What about the money we owe?

00:13:38.150 --> 00:13:40.485
We'll find a way.

00:13:42.071 --> 00:13:44.740
Things will blow over soon.

00:13:44.740 --> 00:13:46.742
Let's think about it, okay?

00:13:47.618 --> 00:13:50.579
Okay, bye.

00:14:08.973 --> 00:14:10.390
Welcome.

00:14:25.698 --> 00:14:27.491
Why did you do to my grandma?

00:14:28.492 --> 00:14:30.870
What did you tell her?

00:14:30.870 --> 00:14:32.830
Your phone was off.

00:14:32.830 --> 00:14:35.291
I couldn't find you at your rental.

00:14:35.291 --> 00:14:37.376
So, I had to go to your hometown.

00:14:37.376 --> 00:14:41.213
So, you're using this dirty trick
to force me to contact you?

00:14:41.213 --> 00:14:44.557
I'm not so scheming as to use an old lady.

00:14:45.551 --> 00:14:50.180
I heard from your grandma
that you two are very close.

00:14:51.807 --> 00:14:53.851
So, you should think about her.

00:14:53.851 --> 00:14:56.882
She'd be so sad if she knew you broke the law.

00:15:11.619 --> 00:15:15.664
Why did you send this to me?

00:15:15.664 --> 00:15:19.043
I want you to know what kind
of person Qian Xiao An is.

00:15:19.043 --> 00:15:23.756
He used you as a scapegoat
and ditched you when things went wrong.

00:15:23.756 --> 00:15:27.057
I know it sounds cruel, but to him...

00:15:27.718 --> 00:15:30.470
you're just someone who can
be replaced at any time.

00:15:48.030 --> 00:15:50.073
I was once like you.

00:15:51.909 --> 00:15:54.328
I fell in love with a man.

00:15:54.328 --> 00:15:56.538
I would do anything for him.

00:15:59.458 --> 00:16:01.919
He was taking the bar exam at that time.

00:16:01.919 --> 00:16:04.129
I let him stay at my place to save money.

00:16:04.129 --> 00:16:06.131
I even lent him a lot of money.

00:16:09.051 --> 00:16:12.679
In the end, I saw him sleeping
with another woman at my place.

00:16:13.305 --> 00:16:15.557
He even married that woman.

00:16:18.644 --> 00:16:20.358
He's gone.

00:16:21.939 --> 00:16:24.066
I can't get my money back.

00:16:25.150 --> 00:16:27.319
I'm not like you.

00:16:27.319 --> 00:16:30.535
He'll give me whatever I want.

00:16:32.533 --> 00:16:36.334
Are you really willing to bet
everything on this man?

00:16:41.875 --> 00:16:44.628
I've discussed it with the chairman.

00:16:44.628 --> 00:16:47.965
As long as you hand over Qian Xiao An's ledger
and account book for the rebates,

00:16:47.965 --> 00:16:50.675
we'll hire a lawyer to help you.

00:16:51.844 --> 00:16:56.056
What will you gain by doing all this?

00:16:56.056 --> 00:16:59.351
I just don't want you to end up with nothing.

00:16:59.351 --> 00:17:03.115
Believe me, it's too tiring to live like that.

00:17:05.190 --> 00:17:07.108
You're the one who's tired.

00:17:08.068 --> 00:17:10.232
If there's nothing else, I'll get going.

00:17:10.904 --> 00:17:13.042
Thank you for sharing your story.

00:17:32.051 --> 00:17:34.316
It feels like I haven't
been here for a long time.

00:17:35.554 --> 00:17:37.681
I remember in the past,

00:17:37.681 --> 00:17:40.792
Shu Juan and I used to sit here
for afternoon tea.

00:17:45.773 --> 00:17:49.150
Ms. Qian, cut to the chase.

00:17:52.029 --> 00:17:54.698
You're not even in a hurry
to explain to the media.

00:17:54.698 --> 00:17:56.997
What's there to be anxious about?

00:18:08.879 --> 00:18:11.340
If you can't produce the DNA paternity report,

00:18:11.340 --> 00:18:13.592
you must have your reasons.

00:18:13.592 --> 00:18:15.294
Frankly speaking,

00:18:15.294 --> 00:18:18.900
I don't care whose child you're carrying.

00:18:20.265 --> 00:18:24.228
All I want is Hongfa's management rights.

00:18:24.228 --> 00:18:25.938
So?

00:18:25.938 --> 00:18:28.732
If you voluntarily resign
as Hongfa's chairperson,

00:18:28.732 --> 00:18:31.610
I'll immediately end the union's protest.

00:18:31.610 --> 00:18:35.239
The board won't force you to explain anymore.

00:18:35.239 --> 00:18:37.741
Once we reach a consensus within the company,

00:18:37.741 --> 00:18:40.577
public opinion will naturally calm down.

00:18:40.577 --> 00:18:42.204
This way,

00:18:42.204 --> 00:18:45.916
you can still keep your position
as a board member and your income.

00:18:45.916 --> 00:18:49.153
From now on, whoever you want to be with,

00:18:49.153 --> 00:18:51.437
or what kind of life you want,

00:18:51.437 --> 00:18:53.406
no one will bother you.

00:18:54.216 --> 00:18:57.639
Is that clear enough?

00:19:08.981 --> 00:19:10.501
Are you still busy?

00:19:12.484 --> 00:19:14.319
It's so late. Why are you still here?

00:19:14.319 --> 00:19:18.323
The Chaomai Public Acquisition Team's
strategy meeting just ended.

00:19:18.323 --> 00:19:20.079
Thank you for your hard work.

00:19:23.412 --> 00:19:26.034
There's something I want to tell you.

00:19:27.166 --> 00:19:29.459
About you and Xin Yi Fu...

00:19:29.459 --> 00:19:31.570
The chairwoman told me everything.

00:19:33.172 --> 00:19:35.591
I called Shi Weekly today.

00:19:35.591 --> 00:19:39.761
My high-ranking friend and I
discussed the chairwoman's article.

00:19:39.761 --> 00:19:42.639
I accidentally heard some funny news.

00:19:43.432 --> 00:19:44.975
What is it?

00:19:44.975 --> 00:19:46.852
My friend said...

00:19:46.852 --> 00:19:49.780
The paparazzi photos and reports

00:19:49.780 --> 00:19:53.066
of Xin Yi Fu and Lin Xi Ming's
daughter on a date...

00:19:53.066 --> 00:19:56.083
were actually arranged by Qian Li Hua.

00:19:59.114 --> 00:20:04.119
I think she wanted to make you angry.

00:20:04.119 --> 00:20:06.538
She wanted you to leave Xin Yi Fu.

00:21:31.415 --> 00:21:32.987
You're up.

00:21:40.048 --> 00:21:42.002
Come, let's have breakfast.

00:22:00.193 --> 00:22:01.486
