I have kleptomania.

00:29:37.025 --> 00:29:38.109
What?

00:29:38.109 --> 00:29:40.028
I have kleptomania.

00:29:40.028 --> 00:29:41.657
It's an illness.

00:29:44.032 --> 00:29:46.951
Please find my psychiatrist for me.

00:29:46.951 --> 00:29:49.204
His name is Gu Hou Ze.

00:29:49.204 --> 00:29:50.997
Please contact him for me.

00:29:51.664 --> 00:29:53.541
Ask him to come, all right?

00:30:02.425 --> 00:30:03.968
Hello, I'm calling from Kangle Police Station.

00:30:03.968 --> 00:30:05.178
My name is Zhang.

00:30:05.178 --> 00:30:08.180
Are you Zhou Xiao Qi's psychiatrist?

00:30:09.265 --> 00:30:12.894
Zhou Xiao Qi stole a lot of things
from a shop on Xin'an Road.

00:30:12.894 --> 00:30:15.645
The shop reported it. She's with us now.

00:30:17.982 --> 00:30:19.192
I see.

00:30:19.192 --> 00:30:21.444
Okay, I understand. Thank you.

00:30:23.112 --> 00:30:24.697
What did he say?

00:30:24.697 --> 00:30:27.658
He said you're no longer his patient.

00:30:31.120 --> 00:30:33.982
Is there anyone else you can contact?

00:30:41.548 --> 00:30:44.091
I'm not his patient.

00:31:00.233 --> 00:31:02.485
Pack your bags.

00:31:02.485 --> 00:31:05.280
I'll pick you up later.

00:31:05.280 --> 00:31:06.655
Do you hear me?

00:31:08.867 --> 00:31:11.535
- Hello, Sis.
- Have you seen the news?

00:31:13.121 --> 00:31:16.082
Yes, I saw it. I've asked
the union to withdraw.

00:31:16.082 --> 00:31:18.793
She just agreed to resign this afternoon.

00:31:18.793 --> 00:31:22.672
Tonight, that doctor revealed a paternity test.

00:31:22.672 --> 00:31:25.925
If Mr. Wu sees the news,
he'll turn to Zhou Xiao Qi again.

00:31:25.925 --> 00:31:27.760
Don't worry. Hear me out.

00:31:27.760 --> 00:31:29.804
As long as we keep buying Hongfa,

00:31:29.804 --> 00:31:32.557
and Mr. Huang and Lin Xi Ming's
shares add up to more than half,

00:31:32.557 --> 00:31:35.351
even if Zhou Xiao Qi proves
the child is Mr. Zhan's,

00:31:35.351 --> 00:31:37.228
it's useless.

00:31:38.313 --> 00:31:40.022
Zhou Xiao Qi...

00:31:40.690 --> 00:31:42.317
What is she up to?

00:31:42.317 --> 00:31:45.320
Sis, it's rare for you to be so anxious.

00:31:45.320 --> 00:31:46.654
Listen, I'll take care of everything.

00:31:46.654 --> 00:31:48.197
Just relax, okay?

00:31:48.197 --> 00:31:49.407
Okay, that's all for now.

00:31:49.407 --> 00:31:50.408
I have something to take care of.

00:31:50.408 --> 00:31:52.562
Alright, bye.

00:32:56.307 --> 00:32:58.100
Have you sorted it all out?

00:33:02.855 --> 00:33:06.651
What will happen to
the Vice President if I give it to you?

00:33:06.651 --> 00:33:08.694
