00:33:17.453 --> 00:33:19.497
from my time with Qian Xiao An.

00:33:19.497 --> 00:33:21.332
All the companies that took kickbacks,

00:33:21.332 --> 00:33:24.627
the contacts, the amounts,

00:33:24.627 --> 00:33:27.255
and the exact times
Qian Xiao An received money.

00:33:27.255 --> 00:33:29.006
It's all recorded here.

00:33:38.099 --> 00:33:39.600
Surprised?

00:33:41.352 --> 00:33:43.395
I'm not as stupid as you think.

00:33:45.732 --> 00:33:47.441
What will you do next?

00:33:50.194 --> 00:33:52.203
We'll take legal action.

00:33:53.406 --> 00:33:56.570
We'll discuss the details
with the lawyer and the chairman.

00:33:58.578 --> 00:34:00.028
What about you?

00:34:01.205 --> 00:34:03.374
What's your plan?

00:34:07.962 --> 00:34:09.936
I plan to leave this place.

00:34:12.133 --> 00:34:14.967
I don't want to have anything
to do with you guys anymore.

00:34:18.056 --> 00:34:20.057
Then take care of yourself.

00:34:21.184 --> 00:34:22.601
You, too.

00:34:31.903 --> 00:34:33.237
That's great.

00:34:39.994 --> 00:34:41.829
Xiao Ting Yun, where are you now?

00:34:41.829 --> 00:34:45.116
Listen, call me as soon
as you get this message.

00:34:52.965 --> 00:34:54.152
[I gave all the evidence of
your kickbacks to Secretary Pan.]

00:34:54.152 --> 00:34:55.650
[This is the price you
pay for deceiving me.]

00:35:03.476 --> 00:35:06.395
Sorry, the number you dialed...

00:35:34.507 --> 00:35:37.844
Must you do this to yourself?

00:35:37.844 --> 00:35:40.012
Zhou Xiao Qi!

00:35:40.012 --> 00:35:42.932
Everyone must be responsible
for themselves.

00:35:42.932 --> 00:35:44.809
Listen up.

00:35:44.809 --> 00:35:48.771
This is the last time I'll bail you
out of the police station.

00:35:48.771 --> 00:35:50.638
It won't happen again.

00:36:03.612 --> 00:36:08.975
[Pan Xin Tong]

00:36:13.296 --> 00:36:14.172
Hello.

00:36:14.172 --> 00:36:18.092
Sister Xiao Qi, I got the evidence
of Qian Xiao An taking kickbacks.

00:36:23.931 --> 00:36:25.391
Grandma.

00:36:26.100 --> 00:36:29.103
I told you not to carry
so much at once. It's heavy.

00:36:29.103 --> 00:36:30.730
Let me do it.

00:36:30.730 --> 00:36:32.356
This is for you.

00:36:34.150 --> 00:36:35.765
Why did you suddenly come back?

00:36:35.765 --> 00:36:37.320
Why didn't you tell me?

00:36:37.320 --> 00:36:38.904
I missed you.

00:36:39.947 --> 00:36:41.824
That's not right.

00:36:41.824 --> 00:36:44.235
Didn't the company send you abroad?

00:36:44.911 --> 00:36:46.829
I'm not going.

00:36:46.829 --> 00:36:48.873
Not going? Why?

00:36:48.873 --> 00:36:51.375
What's wrong with work?

00:36:51.375 --> 00:36:53.628
Don't worry so much.

00:36:53.628 --> 00:36:55.630
Isn't it good that I'm back
to keep you company?

00:36:55.630 --> 00:36:57.423
Yes, very good.

00:36:57.423 --> 00:36:58.674
Let's go.

00:36:59.884 --> 00:37:03.536
Let's go home.

