helping me organize them.

00:38:09.537 --> 00:38:11.330
She's so nice.

00:38:11.330 --> 00:38:13.708
I asked her to stay for dinner.

00:38:13.708 --> 00:38:15.686
She even helped me wash the dishes.

00:38:16.836 --> 00:38:19.630
She's a good girl, just like you.

00:40:02.566 --> 00:40:04.051
Pan Xin Tong!

00:40:07.071 --> 00:40:09.281
Where is it? Where is it?

